             was indicted for <rs id="t18030112-63-off342" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030112-63-off342" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030112-63-off342" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18030112-63-cd343" type="crimeDate">14th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030112-63-off342 t18030112-63-cd343"></join>, three handkerchiefs, value 3s. a shirt, value 5s. a pair of stockings, value 2s. four sheets, value 40s. and a counterpane, value 10s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18030112-63-victim463" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Layton
